{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_11_level_main_11-08_beg","storyGroup":"main_11","storySort":102,"storyDependence":"main_11_level_main_11-08_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"11-9","storyName":"以命换命","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"血魔大君烧毁了坎伯兰公爵府，处决多名贵族。为了保护工厂其他人，凯瑟琳选择直面萨卡兹雇佣兵。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_11-08_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_11-08","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["阿勒黛","？？？","市侩的贵族","血魔大君","莱托中校","萨卡兹战士","萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","凯瑟琳","明椒","费斯特"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ghosthunter_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_ghosthunter_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"subtitle","text":"艾尔希，一定有东西不会变！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"比如说，等我长大，我会成为蒸汽骑士，像那位林奇先生一样！不，我会比林奇先生还要厉害！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我会保护你们，把坏人都赶走。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我会像曾曾曾曾祖母一样，让坎伯兰这个名字永远闪耀。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"艾尔希，我保证，我会让你看见的！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","id":14},{"type":"playsound","key":"$burningloop1","volume":"1","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":15},{"type":"image","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","y":"80","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":16},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"5","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":17},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1.05","yScaleTo":"1.05","yTo":"0","duration":"30","block":"false","id":18},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.7","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"艾尔希！！！","id":20},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_doorbreak","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.5","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"坚持住，我，我马上就......","id":22},{"type":"playsound","key":"$firestorm","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"我答应过你的，我......","id":24},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"1","g":"0.5","b":"0.1","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":28},{"type":"image","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"1","y":"-40","block":"false","id":29},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"0.82","yScaleTo":"0.82","yTo":"0","duration":"40","block":"false","id":30},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"阿勒黛，马上离开。","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"血魔在靠近，你不能被发现。","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"艾尔希还在这里，我必须——","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你必须遵守她的命令，她不会允许你自作主张。","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"你，你们不能......","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我们能。我们听从公爵的命令来协助你“完成任务”，不是你的仆人。","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别忘记她是怎么教你的。","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别忘记你的立场。","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"我......","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你必须做的只有一件事，那就是完成你的使命。","id":42},{"type":"text","text":"在某一个瞬间，阿勒黛忘了自己在哪里，身边又站着谁。","id":43},{"type":"text","text":"她很想往前跑，很想冲进那场正在夺走她残余人生的大火里。","id":44},{"type":"text","text":"就像二十六年前的那个夜晚，她想要冲进另一片火光中，阻止议会的士兵带走父亲。","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"至于其他的事，你早就没有资格了。","id":46},{"type":"text","text":"阿勒黛睁大眼睛，她眼中的泪水被火焰烤干了。","id":47},{"type":"text","text":"但她确实无疑地看到，燃烧的花园中，正有一个巨大的身影拔地而起。","id":48},{"type":"text","text":"是那具残损的蒸汽甲胄吗？是曾经凝集着她无数幻想与奢望的蒸汽甲胄吗？","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"回到目标人物的身边，马上。","id":50},{"type":"text","text":"在无数艰难的时刻，阿勒黛用尽全身力气祈祷，希望那位伟大的先祖会重新降临到蒸汽甲胄之上，帮她渡过难关。","id":51},{"type":"text","text":"现在，她看到了，古老的铠甲，正喷吐着最可怖的烈焰。","id":52},{"type":"text","text":"她看见了火焰之中的阴影正对自己咆哮。","id":53},{"type":"text","text":"那不是她的希望，她早已渐行渐远。","id":54},{"type":"text","text":"倘若祖先真的归来——","id":55},{"type":"text","text":"阿勒黛知道，那只会是她的梦魇。","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"......","id":57},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"告诉她。","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿勒黛","text":"我会一如既往，遵循她的意愿。","id":61},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":62},{"type":"stopsound","fadetime":"2","channel":"a","id":63},{"type":"dialog","id":64},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":66},{"type":"image","id":67},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":68,"musicid":1},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_bg_21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":69},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","fadetime":"0.5","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"我、我不明白，大君阁下......","id":73,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"我以为您对我们的招待十分满意......","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"您甚至会偶尔光顾我们的舞会，不是吗？您是喜欢这里的！","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_410_1#8$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"我不得不承认，你们一度给我带来了一些快乐。","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_410_1#1$1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"你们那些小心的谄媚，夸张的示好，都曾让我心生怜爱。","id":79,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"您是不是弄错了什么？我跟大公爵与反抗军绝无一丝一毫的牵扯！我保证......","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"要真的有什么问题，那也是那个姓坎伯兰的女人做的！我可以向您检举她！","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"大人......阁下......什么都好，您行行好吧，想要什么我都可以给您！我的那些收藏品，我的钱，都请您拿去！只求您......","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_410_1#7$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"亲爱的，我要这些做什么？","id":85,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"您不会杀了我的，对吧？我们还可以继续举办那些酒会，您一定还没有尝过我珍藏的酒......","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"莱托中校，我会没事的，对吧，这里是伦蒂尼姆！","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"他们，萨卡兹们只是受到卡文迪许公爵那个倒霉蛋邀请，来保护伦蒂尼姆的，他们从不滥杀无辜，对吧？","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"......","id":91,"figure":["avg_npc_649_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#8$1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"带去前面。","id":93,"figure":["avg_npc_649_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_410_1#1$1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"太吵了。快些开始吧。","id":95,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"开、开始什么？","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"等听到命令，你就往里面跑。","id":99,"figure":["avg_npc_419_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"能顺利跑进房子里，确定里面没有活人的话，你就也能活着出来。","id":100,"figure":["avg_npc_419_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"里面......您是说火里？您让我跑进这么大的火里？不，我不会跑的，我不想被烧死！","id":102,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你会照做的。","id":104,"figure":["avg_npc_419_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_410_1#7$1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"——","id":106,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",6]},{"type":"text","text":"古老的萨卡兹站在维多利亚的心脏上，轻轻抬了抬手指。","id":107},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"5","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":108},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"市侩的贵族","text":"唔呃——！","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":112},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"他没有看清身后在追逐着他的是什么。","id":115},{"type":"text","text":"就像萨卡兹战士说的那样，他的确本能地遵守了指令，拼命往前跑去。","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"前面是火，火里至少还有一丝生机。正在追着他的才是绝对的死亡的气息。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"但他的脚步还是太慌乱，没跑几步就跌倒了。","id":118},{"type":"dialog","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","id":120},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":121},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-100","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_blood","delay":"1","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"255","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"鲜血自他身体内部迸发了出来。","id":128},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_stream_loop","volume":"0.4","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","id":129},{"type":"text","text":"它们不再属于原本的主人，而是成了另一个人的仆从。","id":130},{"type":"text","text":"在他的指挥下扑向面前的大地，扑向崩塌着的宅邸，扑向凶猛的大火，咬碎残垣，吞下残枝，盖住灰烬。","id":131},{"type":"text","text":"血液在行军，而且无人可挡，就连火焰都不行。","id":132},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_410_1#7$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"莱托，他说得对。","id":134,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"我还没尝过他珍藏的酒。","id":135,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"血魔大君","text":"我们该去尝尝的，不是吗？","id":136,"figure":["avg_npc_410_1",6]},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":137},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":138},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":141},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9c/Avg_bg_27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":142},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":143,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_054","fadetime":"1","id":146},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","text":"到了，在这里等着。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_054"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#2$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"隆德，查理......","id":150,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"这里就是你们打算处决我们的地方。","id":152,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_054","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","text":"......你怎么知道的。","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_054"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"这还不简单。","id":156,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#9$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"这两年下来，你们从来没有让工人们知道你们在造什么。","id":158,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"但我们这些领头的工人，却也多多少少知道了一些什么。","id":159,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"最近催得这么紧，恐怕是已经接近尾声了吧，既然如此，我们这些知道太多的人，也就该死了。","id":161,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_054","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","text":"......你刚才骗了我。","id":163,"figure":"avg_npc_054"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"放心，只是处理了一点后事而已。","id":165,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我们这些工人任劳任怨了三年，能掀起什么风浪？","id":166,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_054","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","text":"别想给我耍花招。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_054"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","text":"来几个人，跟我去外面看看。","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_054"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","text":"明椒，给我看着她。","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_054"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"......嗯。","id":172,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"character","id":174},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":175},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_054","id":176},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":177},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":179},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我能抽烟吗？","id":181,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"嗯......可以。","id":183,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"谢谢。","id":185,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":186},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_lighter","volume":"0.7","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":188},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_smokefemale","volume":"1","id":189},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#2$1","id":191},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":192},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"你没有想过逃跑吗？","id":194,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"逃跑？跑去哪里？","id":196,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#7$1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"而且，我如果逃跑了，我工厂里的那些工人就遭殃了，孩子。","id":198,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#4$1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"......","id":200,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#9$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我一直在想，你们会怎么对待我们，看起来，你们上面的人还挺有人情味。","id":202,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#10$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"这样算是......有人情味吗？","id":204,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"给你们下命令的人应该说过，不要在工人里掀起恐慌，所以才会把我们聚集在一起悄悄处理掉吧。","id":206,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"要是我的一条命，能换来更多工人继续活下去，那就这样吧。","id":207,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你以为其他被你们带来的老东西，心里不明白吗？","id":208,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我不明白......","id":210,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#2$1","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"呼......","id":212,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"孩子，你今年几岁？","id":214,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":217},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_bg_32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":218},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"博士，你知道蒸汽骑士的故事吗？","id":223,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","focus":"3","id":225},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"227","text":"知道。"},{"id":"227","text":"听过一些。"}],"values":[],"id":226},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":227,"end":237},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"奶奶曾经是打造蒸汽甲胄的工人。","id":229,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",10]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"对过去的我们来说，这是一种认可。","id":230,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"因为守护这座伦蒂尼姆，守护我们家园的战士，他们的甲胄是由我们的双手打造出来的。","id":232,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我曾经也憧憬着，有一天我能像奶奶那样，能亲眼看见那些伟大的事物诞生......能亲身参与其中。","id":234,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"奶奶经历了很多事，她是看着伦蒂尼姆如何一步步走到现在的。我看得出来她很失望。","id":235,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"但我......我还不想这么快就放弃。","id":237,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",8],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_open_box","volume":"1","id":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":241},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"应该是这个抽屉吧......","id":243,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"暗格，暗格......哦，找到了。","id":245,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"不愧是奶奶，一般人根本没法发现这张桌子被改造过......","id":247,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"这是......我的工牌？","id":249,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",6]},{"type":"playsound","key":"$book_close","volume":"1","id":250},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"还有一本......笔记本？","id":252,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我不知道我写下这些能够给谁看，又有什么意义。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":256},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":257},{"type":"subtitle","text":"哈维死的那年，费斯特还没有出生。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":258},{"type":"subtitle","text":"琳蒂试图理解过他，但最终，她的思念都变成了对我的怨气，她埋怨我没有在那天拦住哈维。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":259},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我没有办法反驳她，我也没有办法责怪她最终抛下费斯特，离开了这个家。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":260},{"type":"subtitle","text":"据说她改嫁了一个好人家，好事。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":261},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我没有告诉过费斯特，我不想让他知道，自己的父亲死在了一场没有带来任何结果的抗议中，而他的母亲，是带着恨离开这个家的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":262},{"type":"subtitle","id":263},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":264},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......","id":266,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":267},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":269},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":270,"musicid":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9c/Avg_bg_27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":271},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":273},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"所以你是在哥伦比亚长大的。","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#9$1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"嗯，我是被我姥姥带大的。","id":277,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我的爸爸妈妈都是佣兵，不过他们都死了。","id":278,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#6$1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"那你为什么还要当佣兵？","id":280,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"因为我要养活我和姥姥呀。","id":282,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",10]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"许多地方都不欢迎萨卡兹，我就只好也来当佣兵了。","id":283,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"好孩子。","id":285,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"所以你也同意你们那个摄政王的做法吗？","id":286,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"你是指占领这座城市吗？","id":288,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#13$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"嗯......我不知道。","id":290,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",12]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我们只是收钱办事，一开始，我都不知道，我们是要来占领这么大的一座城市的。","id":292,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"在哥伦比亚，我们的任务也就是替一些见不得光的商人押送一些货物，或是猎杀野兽。","id":293,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我只记得，我头一回见到格林那么激动，是他跟我说，要是这次能成功，萨卡兹就能过上好日子了。","id":295,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#9$1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"格林？那个爱抽烟的格林吗？","id":297,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#1$1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"啊，是的。","id":299,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"他人呢，有阵子没见到他了。","id":301,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"他死了。","id":303,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#5$1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"......你不难过吗？","id":305,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#12$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"格林告诉过我，对我们雇佣兵来说，生离死别是很正常的事。","id":307,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",11]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#6$1","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"生离死别。哪怕这座城市混乱了这么些年，维多利亚人也一点都不懂萨卡兹啊。","id":309,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"接着，孩子。","id":311,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":312},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"10","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":313},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","id":314},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","id":315},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"什么？","id":317,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",10]},{"type":"dialog","id":318},{"type":"character","id":319},{"type":"text","text":"凯瑟琳从烟盒里掏出了一件小东西，抛给明椒。","id":320},{"type":"text","text":"那样东西小小的，软软的，是毛线织成的，颜色还很鲜艳。","id":321},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#4$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"这......指套......","id":323,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#9$1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"格林......","id":325,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"......是你给那个上了年纪的雇佣兵织的吧？","id":327,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"他食指受过伤，会痛，但也戒不了烟。我见他把这玩意儿藏在烟盒里。","id":328,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"大概他也舍不得用，浪费了你的心意。","id":329,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#9$1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"......","id":331,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"他走的时候，把烟盒给了我，当作那几个月的烟钱。","id":333,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"他从来没跟我提过你，但第一眼见到你，我就明白过来，他心里一直惦记着的孩子是谁。","id":334,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#2$1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我......才不......","id":336,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#9$1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我不知道他对这场战争怎么看。","id":338,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"可是我知道，孩子，他不用说我就知道......你还不理解，战争是什么。","id":340,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":343},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_bg_32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":344},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":346},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","fadetime":"1","id":347},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","id":348},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":350},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我其实有预感，费斯特也会离开。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":351},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他和哈维太像了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":352},{"type":"subtitle","text":"仗着自己那点机灵劲，就觉得自己能够解决眼前的所有问题。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":353},{"type":"subtitle","text":"看着他，我就会想起哈维。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":354},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我会分不清，我心中的失望究竟是源自抗争看不到结果，还是哈维没有认清贵族们的面貌。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":355},{"type":"subtitle","text":"或许兼而有之。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":356},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我还是让费斯特走了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":357},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我知道我拦不住他。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":358},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":359},{"type":"subtitle","id":360},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"博士，在我决定带你回来之前，我想过许多要和奶奶说的话。","id":363,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"我本来以为自己已经有了觉悟，这么长时间，我们经历了足够多。","id":364,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"但我现在觉得，我还是欠她一句道歉。","id":366,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1","focus":"3","id":367},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"370","text":"你们是亲人。"},{"id":"370","text":"她并不需要你的道歉，不是吗？"}],"values":[],"id":369},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":370,"end":375},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"......","id":372,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"凯瑟琳永远都是板着脸的样子，很多人都忘记了，她只是个失去了生活的普通人。","id":374,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",0]},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":375,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":376},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":377},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":378},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":379},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":380},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$rebel_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act11d0d0/m_bat_rebel_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":381,"musicid":4},{"type":"subtitle","text":"萨卡兹们从来不让工人接近工厂的某些区域，但他们无疑正在准备一项危险的武器。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":382},{"type":"subtitle","text":"大公爵的掣肘理应让他们无法获得足够的资源支撑到今天。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":383},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但是，无论是交给工厂加工的资材，还是我能够打听到的他们的处境，都证明他们有一条属于自己的补给线。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":384},{"type":"subtitle","text":"这些原本应该与我无关。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":385},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我能做的，只有保住工厂里的这些人。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":386},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但是——","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":387},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我还是把我不应该记下的东西记了下来。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":388},{"type":"subtitle","text":"或许，我内心深处在想着，如果费斯特有一天来寻求我的帮助的话，我能比当年眼睁睁地看着哈维离开，多做一点吧。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":389},{"type":"subtitle","text":"工人无法靠近那些线索，但是，我太了解这片厂区了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":390},{"type":"subtitle","text":"适合被当作补给线停靠站的只有以下几个地点。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":391},{"type":"subtitle","id":392},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"就是这个，博士！奶奶在地图上圈出了好几个位置——","id":395,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1","focus":"3","id":396},{"type":"dialog","id":397},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"399","text":"这些地点必定戒备森严。"},{"id":"402","text":"希望另一边能有所收获。"}],"values":[],"id":398},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":399,"end":401},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"是的，我们要接近停靠站恐怕很困难。","id":401,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",9]},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":402,"end":404},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"嗯，即使我们无法靠近，奶奶留下的这些信息也足够有帮助了。","id":404,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",9],"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":405},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"虽然想要和奶奶告别。","id":407,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"不过，就留到下次吧。","id":408,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费斯特","text":"博士，我们该回去了。","id":410,"figure":["avg_4072_ironmn_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":411},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":412},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":413},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9c/Avg_bg_27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":414},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#9$1","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"和我一起的雇佣兵，有许多人其实都不清楚我们到底是来为什么而战的。","id":417,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我们只是没有地方去了。哪里都不欢迎我们。","id":418,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"而萨卡兹的王说，我们可以有个归处，可以被统治，可以找到未来。","id":419,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"我和你们之中的一些人相处过，看得出来，他们有些甚至没有参与过真正的战斗。","id":421,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你呢？","id":422,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#10$1","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我会战斗！","id":424,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你杀过人吗，孩子？不是那种明确到可以不用有道德负担的恶徒，而是......人。","id":426,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#4$1","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"......","id":428,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#10$1","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"你是工人，你也没有杀过，不要用这种过来人的口气教训我。","id":430,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你在伦蒂尼姆待了这么久，应该听说过蒸汽甲胄吧？","id":432,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"唔，好像是很厉害的兵器，但是很久没有出现过了。","id":434,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"是的，但那是凶器。","id":436,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#2$1","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"而我曾亲手打造了那一台又一台的凶器。","id":438,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_648_1#1$1","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"但我并不为此感到羞愧，因为那些兵器被用来守护了我生活的土地。","id":440,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯瑟琳","text":"你呢，孩子，你知道你正在为了什么东西而挥动手中的凶器吗？","id":441,"figure":["avg_npc_648_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#15$1","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"我......","id":443,"figure":["avg_4071_peper_1",14]},{"type":"dialog","id":444},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"3","id":445},{"type":"dialog","id":446},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":447},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":448},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":449},{"type":"character","id":450},{"type":"image","id":451}],"characters":["阿勒黛","？？？","市侩的贵族","血魔大君","莱托中校","萨卡兹战士","萨卡兹雇佣兵队长","凯瑟琳","明椒","费斯特"]}